messages.text: Hey there, I'm the assistant of the pharmacy. Who's there ?
Hello, it's from my depot plus house. I'm sorry, I'm a little bit on the move. I'm not sure if I can make it.
Understood. Can you hear me clearly now?
Yeah, I'm from my depot plus house.
Alright. Do you have Ibuprofen 400mg - 30 tablets in stock today?
Yes, I do have ibuprofen 40 milligrams of tablet at $1 per unit. I have 1,000 units and seven days delivery. Sure.
Perfect. What's the minimum order quantity?
There is no minimum quantity but I also have very good product which is a Broth Abandoned Dinosaur which costs 5 euros and I have 1,000 of them and the delivery time is 14 days. Goodbye!
